      "content": "hey can u help me out? i keep seeing stuff about this \"PA Energy Transition Act\" in the news and its kinda confusing lol. basically it says the state is gonna start giving huge tax breaks to solar and wind farms but at the same time they're cutting the subsidies that coal companies currently get. can u just give me a quick, objective summary of the pros and cons of this bill? thanks",
