      "content": "thanks. i noticed u said it's a \"progressive step\"... feels like that might be an opinion tho. if we're being purely objective, what would a critic of the bill say about the \"long-term savings\" part? it seems like there's a big debate about whether those savings actually reach the taxpayers or if it's just more gov spending.",
